snippet.textDisplay: I saw some people criticizing the genre selection of current CS as it is more leaning towards electronic music. But if you don't evolve then at some point you'll left behind. So I agree with Abdullah Siddiqui's statement (GO BTS) its better to evolve the different cultural elements with the new style and make it a new genre. Plus people need to understand CS is now more than just Music, its the visual aspect which enhances the emotions which music wants you to feel. So now, it is a whole package that a STUDIO can bring to your screens!
